I also see text saying 'Custom options let customers choose the product variations they want.' However, I need to check if there are any existing customizable options already configured for this product. I see a LayoutTable (element 2514) which might contain the list of options, but there don't appear to be any specific options listed in the accessibility tree. To properly list all customizable options, I should check if there are any options already defined, and if not, report that to the user.
